<i>noun</i>: 추천 [추천], 천거 [천ː거], 알선 [알썬], 권장 [권ː장], 권유 [궈ː뉴], 권고 [권ː고], 건의서 [거ː늬서/거ː니서], 건의문 [거ː늬문 /거ː니문], 건의 [거ː늬 /거ː니] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>추천 [추천]</dt><br>
<dd>recommendation</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 조건에 알맞은 사람이나 물건을 책임지고 소개함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of responsibly introducing someone or something that meets a certain condition.</dd><br>
<dt>천거 [천ː거]</dt><br>
<dd>recommendation</dd><br>
<dd>사람을 소개하거나 추천함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of introducing or recommending someone.</dd><br>
<dt>알선 [알썬]</dt><br>
<dd>good offices; recommendation</dd><br>
<dd>남의 일이 잘되도록 알아봐 주고 도와줌.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of assisting someone's business by saying good things or introducing people.</dd><br>
<dt>권장 [권ː장]</dt><br>
<dd>recommendation; encouragement</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 권하고 장려함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of advising and encouraging someone to do something.</dd><br>
<dt>권유 [궈ː뉴]</dt><br>
<dd>recommendation</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것을 하라고 권함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of advising to do something.</dd><br>
<dt>권고 [권ː고]</dt><br>
<dd>recommendation</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 하도록 동의를 구하며 충고함. 또는 그런 말.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of suggesting while asking for agreement to do something, or such a suggestion.</dd><br>
<dt>건의서 [거ː늬서/거ː니서]</dt><br>
<dd>petition; memorial; representation; recommendation</dd><br>
<dd>건의의 내용을 적은 문서.</dd><br>
<dd>A document containing details of a petition, memorial, or a recommendation.</dd><br>
<dt>건의문 [거ː늬문 /거ː니문]</dt><br>
<dd>proposal; suggestion; recommendation</dd><br>
<dd>건의의 내용을 적은 글.</dd><br>
<dd>Written proposal or suggestions.</dd><br>
<dt>건의 [거ː늬 /거ː니]</dt><br>
<dd>proposal; suggestion; recommendation</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 문제에 대하여 의견이나 바라는 사항을 제시함. 또는 그 의견이나 바라는 사항.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of presenting officially one's opinion or request regarding a certain issue; such an opinion or request.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>